Package com.virginmoneygiving.connect.sdk.v1.beans.fundraiser.request

Bean classes which represent the business objects sent to the VMG /fundraisers/v1/ API.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AuthorisationCodeDetails Bean to hold authorisation code details, which will be exchanged for an access token.
CharitySplit Bean to hold details for what percenatage of donations a single charity will receive on new fundraiser page.
FundraiserAccount Bean to hold fundraiser details for a new Fundraiser Account.
FundraiserPage Bean to hold details for a new fundraiser page.
FundraiserSearchCriteria Bean class to pass search parameters to the Search fundraisers API call via ConnectFundraiserAPI.searchFundraisers(FundraiserSearchCriteria)
